title: The Prime Ministers - series 2 (BBC Radio 4 Documentary)
description:
The Prime Ministers - series 2

Nick Robinson explores how Britain's prime ministers have used their power, responded to the challenges of their time and made the job what it is today.



Episode 1: William Pitt the Younger



Episode 2: Earl Grey



Episode 3: William Gladstone



Episode 4: Herbert Asquith



Episode 5: Ramsay MacDonald



Episode 6: Harold Macmillan



Episode 7: Harold Wilson



Episode 8: Edward Heath
